All Implemented Interfaces:
Destructible, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class UserPlane extends FighterPlane
UserPlane class represents user's plane in game. UserPlane class extends FighterPlane class and implements specific behaviors for user's plane, such as strategies for movement and firing.

    • UserPlane

      public UserPlane(int initialHealth, double screenWidth, ProjectilesFactory projectilesFactory, ComponentsFactory factory, ImgAssetLoader assetLoader, AudioManager audioManager)
      Constructs new UserPlane instance. Initialises user's plane with its image, movement and firing strategies and the audio manager.
      Parameters:
      initialHealth - : initial health of user's plane.
      screenWidth - : width of the screen.
      projectilesFactory - : ProjectilesFactory used for projectiles creation.
      factory - : ComponentsFactory used for components creation.
      assetLoader - : ImgAssetLoader used for loading images.
      audioManager - : AudioManager used for playing audio.
